    <item>
      <title>中国酒巨头Moutai认为年收入增长缓慢</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-liquor-giant-moutai-sees-annual-revenue-growth-slow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Kweichow Moutai Co.报告说，2024年的收入增长速度较慢，因为中国酒类制造商收紧了库存控制，以解决其旗舰精神的价格波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-liquor-giant-moutai-sees-annual-revenue-growth-slow</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 13:48:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
